{"lastModified":1769788293751,"uri":"c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: West Mediterranean -Naples/Sicily, Riviera/Corsica/Sardinia\nWinter Operating Area: Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nL'OCTANT is a 15.60m / 51ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2018 by Neel Trimarans and later underwent a refit in 2022. Sleeping 6 guests in 3 cabins and with a crew of 2. Cruising at 9.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 12.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise a Master cabin with a king size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities and 2 queen cabins with queen size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"L'OCTANT","images":["/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::nSvX_Xnl0.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::yachts-101904-0aHJYlZvM.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::yachts-101904-jqMbcV-Vx.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::yachts-101904-z-TfixhELP.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::yachts-101904-OFQbObZAo.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::yachts-101904-rK-bbyuXZ.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d5c3a5a0-bf4d-11ee-918e-b5a5583b34c9.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::yachts-101904-4dO9CxMTNS.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458be-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::yachts-101904-bCAAumip-P.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8183534776::vessel::779458