 Conditioning","quantity":""},{"label":"WIFI","quantity":""},{"label":"Salon TV","quantity":""},{"label":"Children Allowed","quantity":""},{"label":"Generator","quantity":""},{"label":"Salon Stereo","quantity":""},{"label":"Hairdryers","quantity":""},{"label":"Inverter","quantity":""},{"label":"BBQ","quantity":""},{"label":"Sailing Instructions","quantity":""},{"label":"Deck shower","quantity":""},{"label":"Water Maker","quantity":""},{"label":"Bimini","quantity":""},{"label":"Solar panels","quantity":""},{"label":"CD Player","quantity":""},{"label":"Apple TV","quantity":""},{"label":"Audio System","quantity":""}],"toys":[{"label":"Dinghy","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Paddle-boards Stand Up (SUP)","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Fishing Equipments","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Boarding Ladder","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Snorkeling Equipment","quantity":"7"},{"label":"Sea Scotter","quantity":"1"}],"entertainment":["WIFI","Salon TV","Salon Stereo","Apple TV","Audio System","CD Player","Hifi Fusion MS AV 750"],"tenders":["Highfield Ultra Light 3.4m with 10hp"]},"crew":[{"name":"Antoine Poette","role":"Captain","bio":"Antoine is an experienced catamaran sailor with trips throughout the Mediterranean, French Guiana, and the Caribbean. \nAbundant in local knowledge, he can show you the calanques like no one else and is familiar with all the anchorages and wild bays on Corsica. He is a passionate sailor who will make sure you have a great time sailing this comfortable and performant trimaran."},{"name":"Maryline Poette","role":"Captain","bio":"Having chosen to concentrate on the culinary arts and pleasing gourmets on board yachts, Maryline is first and foremost a wonderful assistance to her captain, having earned a diploma as a captain herself. She completed her training in French cooking in Perpignan and has been entertaining guests on the Octant for nearly two years. \nYou'll enjoy your stay with them aboard L'Octant since she loves to pour her generosity into her cuisine, which are 